<quantity id="4CC04A896663FFD3FEDC009669889FB0" box="[320,470,1926,1953]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.675" metricValueMax="5.5" metricValueMin="1.85" pageId="5" pageNumber="286" unit="m" value="367.5" valueMax="550.0" valueMin="185.0">185 to 550 m</quantity>
, although NMFS SEFSC trawl surveys have reported this species as shallow as 
<quantity id="4CC04A896663FFD3FACA00966DC29FB0" box="[1366,1436,1926,1953]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.25" pageId="5" pageNumber="286" unit="m" value="125.0">125 m</quantity>
depth.
</paragraph>
